RITEK Corporation





Type

Public[1]


Industry
Computer Hardware
Optical Media, Flash Memory, Green Product


Founded
December 29, 1988


Headquarters
Hsinchu Industrial Park, Taiwan



Key people

Founder：Jintai Yeh
Chairman：Gorden Yeh
Vice President：Jennifer Yang


Products
Optical Storage, Flash Memory, Portable Hard-Drive, PV Module & System ,PMOLED Display, ITO Glass, Touch Panel, NANO-Technology Product, BIO-Technology Product, Plastic Product


Revenue
